Higher Education Minister, Blade Nzimande says his department has requested an explanation. #DStv403​ #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Higher Education Minister, Blade Nzimande, says his department has requested an explanation after 35-year-old Mthokozisi Ntumba died on Wednesday. READ: WATCH: Nzimande unpacks decision on NSFAS "I have directed Wits University council and management, and the relevant law enforcement agencies to provide us with an explanation on how this tragedy happened," Nzimande says. The minister also says student funding should be prioritised. Ntumba was shot during student protests. He was married and had just completed his master's degree. Watch the video above for more details on this story.